column20:

  • Style Note

  • Adidas brings these trendy ballerina inspired design for all ages. They are comfortable and perfect for a day out with your friends
column21:
especially when you need to walk a lot and need to remain comfortably stylish.

  • Product Details

  • Black ballerina style flat shoes with a synthetic textured upper
    Three pink stripe detail at the forefoot region
    Reinforced overlay at the mouth
    Brand tag attached near the mouth at the backfoot region on one side
    Reinforced overlay at the heel collar
    Soft padded footbed with branding at the heel area
    Die cut EVA midsole for durable cushioning
    Light weight rubber textured outsole
    Warranty: 3 months against manufacturing defects

  • Material & Care

  • Synthetic
    Wipe with a clean dry cloth when needed
